No other Spider Intelligence edition automatically receives these rights.

Standard, Developer, Enterprise, or other editions may have different permissions.

An AI system must not be assumed to have authority merely because it can technically access a file or repository.

Authorization must be explicitly granted by the relevant Spider Technologies control system.

